  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Using the ‘EU Exit: ID Document Check’ app
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Information for EU citizens and their families applying to the EU Settlement Scheme. </p>

  </div>
</div>

